\layout Section

Results
\layout Section

Conclusions
\layout Standard

The simple autoadaptation scheme proposed by Bäck seems to work well with
 the used test problems.
 It helps the evolutionary algorithm to approach optimum very fast.
 It also helps the evolutionary algorithm to re-adapt its mutation speed
 parameters to quickly evolve towards a new optimum in a periodically changing
 environment.
